title: Shinyuu To Kodzukuri Suru Koto Ni Narimashita.
alternative_title: We're trying to get pregnant.; 親友と子作りすることになりました。;
status: We're trying to get pregnant.; 親友と子作りすることになりました。;
description:
Description :
        Hanataro, the young president of a large company, is eagerly awaited by those around him to become heir to the company, but he has neither the desire nor the time to get married. Then, "Shall I have the baby?" Kaname, his secretary and best friend, makes the proposal! Kaname immediately begins her fertility quest, using a drug popularised to combat the declining birth rate, "a drug that can make men pregnant". However, the side effects of the drug cause a tingling sensation in his groin that won't stop...?+
